 
 *   Ideja zadatka je da se napravi Rent-A-Car aplikacija.

 *   U klasi Korisnik se definise ime korisnika koji iznajmljuje ili vraca automobil u agenciju.

 *   Agencija ima 4 klasicna automobila i SAMO jedan dzip.

 *   Za kreiranje Dzipa je koriscen Singleton Design Pattern.

 *   Svi automobili su ubaceni u listu i svaka operacija se odrazava na stanje liste u zavisnosti da li je automobil izdat ili ne.
 
 *   Na kraju ubaciti izbor jezika.
 
 _____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
 
 *   I made a simulation of Rent-A-Car aplication.
 
 *   In Korisnik class is defined name of a user who wants to rent or return back a vehicle.
 
 *   The agency has 4 regular vehicles and JUST ONE SUV.
 
 *   For creating an SUV I used Singleton Design Pattern.
 
 *   All vehicles (including SUV) are stored in ArrayList. All operations are affecting on list and has an option to show current situation.
 
 *   At the end of the program, I made an option for selecting a language of application.